<% @title = "About - Price Tracker" %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Price Scraping Tool (Price Tracker)</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            A Project to scrape prices from websites and track them.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What is this project?</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                This is a Ruby-based web scraping project that pulls data from popular e-commerce websites.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Tech Stack</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Ruby with Sinatra framework</li>
                <li><strong>Database:</strong> JSON for data persistence</li>
                <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript</li>
                <li><strong>Web Scraping:</strong> Nokogiri and HTTParty gems</li>
                <li><strong>Templates:</strong> ERB (Embedded Ruby)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Key Features</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li>Hybrid price tracking (web scraping + manual entry)</li>
                <li>Price history visualization</li>
                <li>Intelligent price validation</li>
                <li>Responsive design for all devices</li>
                <li>RESTful API endpoints</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6">
